raphic dynamics in younger successional forests, and factors influencing recruitment limitation.},
	language = {en},
	number = {12},
	urldate = {2025-01-31},
	journal = {Global Ecology and Biogeography},
	author = {Duncanson, Laura I. and Dubayah, Ralph O. and Enquist, Brian J.},
	year = {2015},
